			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="short">
							<a class="options btn btn-default btn-mini btn-xs" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2168478)" c>Unfold</a>
						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2168478)">So, dystopias and stuff.</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dillinger-phd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005876); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005876&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164745" alt="Dillinger PhD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005876)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dillinger-phd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005876); return false;" >Dillinger PhD</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1417249729 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">29 Nov 2014 08:28</span>
		</div>
